           Error of intensity value for 1077.34 keV gamma-line
           is 0.0003.
ERR-ANALYS (ERR-T) The total uncertainty of the cross-section
           values ranging from 6 % to 11 % was calculated as the
           square root of the sum of the squares of the
           individual errors:
           (ERR-1,3.,5.) detector efficiency;
           (ERR-2,1.,3.) the area under the spectrometric peak;
           (ERR-3) target thickness;
           (ERR-4,4.,8.) beam intensity;
           (ERR-5,,5.) decay data.
